parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS module can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to a loss of control, accidents, and potentially fatal consequences.
symptoms: The front or rear brake lever becomes frozen or stuck
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal does not return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to stop or slow down.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake fluid leaks can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to a loss of control, accidents, and potentially fatal consequences.
symptoms: Brake fluid dripping from under the motor
soft or spongy brake pedal
brake pedal feels like it's going to the floor
brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position.

brake fluid leaking from under the motor

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the compensator sprocket assembly can cause loud banging noises, loss of power, and unexpected acceleration, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Loud banging noises on start-up
especially when the engine is hot
loss of power
unexpected acceleration
vibration
and skidding.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Throttle and Carburetor Wire Harness Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle and carburetor wire harness can cause the motorcycle to lose power and accelerate unexpectedly, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Sudden loss of power
unexpected acceleration
and inability to shift gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic throttle control system can cause the motorcycle to accelerate on its own, leading to a loss of control and potentially causing accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The motorcycle accelerates on its own
the throttle sticks
the motorcycle idles at high RPM
the motorcycle slows down to 2000 RPM when coming to a stop
the motorcycle has intermittent idle issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the motorcycle to stall, leading to a loss of control and potentially causing accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The motorcycle stalls without warning
the fuel filter housing breaks

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed or Unavailable Repairs for Fuel System Recall
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of repairs for the fuel system recall can cause the motorcycle to remain in an unsafe condition, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The dealer is unable to repair the motorcycle due to unavailable parts
